<h2>After Judgment: Enforcement Options</h2>

<p>
If you obtain judgment but the defendant does not pay, you can enforce the judgment using:
</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Warrant of Control (N323)</strong> — Bailiffs collect the debt</li>
  <li><strong>Attachment of Earnings (N337)</strong> — Money deducted from defendant's wages</li>
  <li><strong>Third Party Debt Order (N379)</strong> — Freeze defendant's bank account</li>
  <li><strong>Charging Order (N380)</strong> — Secure the debt against defendant's property</li>
</ul>

<p>
See the <strong>Enforcement Guide</strong> (included in this pack) for details.
</p>

